```java
public class GoogleSatelliteDemo extends GisDemoPane {
	public GoogleSatelliteDemo() {
		init();
	}
	void init() {
		try {
			createCity();
		} catch (IOException e) {
			e.printStackTrace();
		}
		// createPolyline();
		// createRiver();
		this.network.setTileSource(new GoogleSatelliteTileSource());
		this.network.setShowStatusBar(true);
	}
	void createCity() throws IOException {
		Properties properties = new Properties();
		properties.load(this.getClass().getResourceAsStream("city.properties"));
		Enumeration<?> propertyNames = properties.propertyNames();
		while (propertyNames.hasMoreElements()) {
			String key = (String) propertyNames.nextElement();
			String property = properties.getProperty(key);
			String tokens[] = property.split(",");
			double lon = Double.parseDouble(tokens[0]);
			double lat = Double.parseDouble(tokens[1]);
			ResizableNode node = new ResizableNode();
			node.setDisplayName(key);
			node.setGeoPosition(new Point3D(lat, lon));
			node.putCustomDraw(true);
			node.setSize(15, 15);
			node.putCustomDrawFillColor(BladeUtil.getRandomColor());
			node.putLabelColor(BladeUtil.getRandomColor());
			box.addElement(node);
		}
	}
	public static void main(String argv[]) {
		// MapComponent mapComponent = new MapComponent();
		// mapComponent.setTileSource(new ArcGISTileSource());
		// GisDemoUtil.show(mapComponent);
		GisDemoUtil.show(new GoogleSatelliteDemo());
	}
}
```
